	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello<br>Wieght is important,in other words you want to carry as little as possible.I am a level 44 wood elf ranger and with all my gear my Wieght to Streight ratio is around .4 to 1.With all my STR gear im at around 145 and i dont like to carry more then around 60.I think its like monks where they dont like to carry more then around 12,this i believe is because the more you carry the less agile you are and will take more damage.Of course we ranger cannot hope to carry 12 with all of our weapons and armor but the less you carry the better of you might be.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
